        <a href="https://arxiv.org/pdf/2109.05603.pdf" class="text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-600 transition-colors underline decoration-1 underline-offset-2">pdf</a>
        <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2109.05603" class="text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-600 transition-colors underline decoration-1 underline-offset-2">arXiv</a>
        <a href="https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/9691818" class="text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-600 transition-colors underline decoration-1 underline-offset-2">IEEE</a>
